This hits me a little hard because ive had seizures from the same things, no one ever takes them seriously, even though ive had stitches in my eyelid from falling on my face and things like that.
I can't believe they put narcan up his nose but they didnt give him any anticonvulsants to stop the seizing???? Just the narcan while seizing wouldve sent his body into full withdrawal and overwhelmed his body which probably helped cause the cardiac arrest.. opiates and opioids don't cause seizures too btw. I'm so sorry about his passing, another up and coming unique talent gone. I really hope ppl will take things like this more seriously. No one ever cares until it's too late......
